'''International Environment Photographers Association''' is an organization based in [[Japan]] focusing global environment issues through photographic activities. Their goal is to make people aware about climate changes and conscious of environmental protection. They held their 1st international exhibition at Amusement Sado in [[Sado, Niigata|Sado]], [[Niigata Prefecture|Niigata]], Japan from 15 to 29 November 2009.<ref>http://www.theiepa.org/sado/report.html</ref>

Their philosophy is "Beautiful, natural landscape is deeply connected to the spiritual wealth of human beings."

